@baseUrl = http://localhost:5500
@studentToken = <pegar_token_de_sesion_clerk_del_estudiante>
@measurementId = <id_de_la_medida>

### Registrar medida corporal (onboarding o seguimiento)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/body-measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weightKg": 72.5,
  "heightCm": 175,
  "measuredAt": "2026-06-29",
  "chestCm": 98,
  "waistCm": 82,
  "hipCm": 95,
  "armCm": 32,
  "bicepCm": 35
}

### Actualizar una medida específica
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/body-measurements/{{measurementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weightKg": 71.8,
  "waistCm": 80
}

### Listar historial de medidas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/body-measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
